---
import SectionCard from '../SectionCard.astro';
---

<section class="slide slide-landing">
  <div class="landing-content">
    <div class="landing-header">
      <h1 class="landing-title">JavaScript Asíncrono</h1>
      <p class="landing-subtitle">Dos modelos para ejecutar tareas sin bloquear la interfaz de usuario</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Distinción conceptual -->
    <div class="concept-comparison" aria-label="Comparación de enfoques">
      <div class="concept-item">
        <div class="concept-diagram concurrency-diagram" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="thread-row">
            <span class="thread-label">Hilo</span>
            <div class="task-blocks">
              <span class="task-block task-a">A</span>
              <span class="task-block task-b">B</span>
              <span class="task-block task-a">A</span>
              <span class="task-block task-b">B</span>
              <span class="task-block task-a">A</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="concept-label">Concurrencia — un hilo, tareas intercaladas</p>
      </div>

      <div class="concept-divider" aria-hidden="true">vs</div>

      <div class="concept-item">
        <div class="concept-diagram parallelism-diagram" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="thread-row">
            <span class="thread-label">Hilo 1</span>
            <div class="task-blocks">
              <span class="task-block task-a">A</span>
              <span class="task-block task-a">A</span>
              <span class="task-block task-a">A</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="thread-row">
            <span class="thread-label">Hilo 2</span>
            <div class="task-blocks">
              <span class="task-block task-b">B</span>
              <span class="task-block task-b">B</span>
              <span class="task-block task-b">B</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="concept-label">Paralelismo — múltiples hilos, tareas simultáneas</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Cards de sección -->
    <div class="cards-row">
      <SectionCard
        title="Event Loop"
        description="Concurrencia cooperativa en un solo hilo. Aprende cómo JavaScript gestiona tareas asíncronas con el Call Stack, Web APIs, Callback Queue y Microtask Queue."
        targetIndex={1}
        accentColor="var(--color-accent)"
        ariaLabel="Ir a la sección Event Loop"
      />
      <SectionCard
        title="Web Workers"
        description="Paralelismo real con múltiples hilos. Descubre cómo ejecutar código CPU-intensivo en segundo plano sin bloquear la interfaz de usuario."
        targetIndex={9}
        accentColor="var(--color-worker-thread, #F472B6)"
        ariaLabel="Ir a la sección Web Workers"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .slide-landing {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    height: 100%;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 30%, #1a1a3a 0%, var(--color-bg) 70%);
    overflow-y: auto;
  }

  .landing-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-8);
    padding: var(--space-10) var(--space-8);
    max-width: 900px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .landing-header {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .landing-title {
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    font-weight: 800;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #38BDF8, #F472B6);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .landing-subtitle {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  /* ── Comparación conceptual ── */
  .concept-comparison {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-5) var(--space-8);
    width: 100%;
  }

  .concept-item {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .concept-divider {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .concept-diagram {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    width: 100%;
  }

  .thread-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }

  .thread-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    min-width: 3.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .task-blocks {
    display: flex;
    gap: 3px;
  }

  .task-block {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 28px;
    height: 20px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .task-a {
    background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.2);
    border: 1px solid #38BDF8;
    color: #38BDF8;
  }

  .task-b {
    background: rgba(244, 114, 182, 0.2);
    border: 1px solid #F472B6;
    color: #F472B6;
  }

  .concept-label {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  /* ── Cards ── */
  .cards-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    width: 100%;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .cards-row :global(.section-card) {
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 380px;
  }
</style>
